  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">Assam experiences monsoon (May-September), moderate winter (October-February) and warm summer (March-April). October to March offers ideal weather for tourism with clear skies, comfortable temperatures and excellent visibility for wildlife viewing and outdoor activities.</p>
